ru.nordavind.ecgdonglelib

Annotation Type FailedToStartScanReason


  • @Target(value={FIELD,LOCAL_VARIABLE,METHOD,PARAMETER})
 @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface FailedToStartScanReason
    reasons why we were unable to start scan

    • Field Detail

      • DEVICE_DISCONNECTED

        public static final int DEVICE_DISCONNECTED
        device is not connected at the time ECG Dongle framework received StartScan message

      • SDK_ERROR_CANT_CREATE_SCANNER

        public static final int SDK_ERROR_CANT_CREATE_SCANNER
        Error creating scan runner. Some Framework issue

      • SDK_ERROR_CANT_CREATE_SOCKET

        public static final int SDK_ERROR_CANT_CREATE_SOCKET
        error creating socket to transfer chunks between ECG Dongle Framework and ServiceWrapper

      • SCAN_START_TIMED_OUT

        public static final int SCAN_START_TIMED_OUT
        Timed out while starting ECG Dongle scan

      • ERROR_ACCEPTING_SOCKET

        public static final int ERROR_ACCEPTING_SOCKET
        got IO Exception when accepting socket used to transfer chunks between ECG Dongle Framework and ServiceWrapper

      • STOP_REQUESTED_BEFORE_SCAN_START

        public static final int STOP_REQUESTED_BEFORE_SCAN_START
        StopScan() was called before ECG Dongle Scan really started

      • EXCEPTION_WRITING_DATA_CHUNK

        public static final int EXCEPTION_WRITING_DATA_CHUNK
        failed wo write DongleDataChunk to socket used to transfer chunks between ECG Dongle Framework and ServiceWrapper

      • NO_SUBSCRIPTION

        public static final int NO_SUBSCRIPTION
        active subscription is required to start scan with this device. No active subscruiption found

      • DEVICE_STOPPED

        public static final int DEVICE_STOPPED
        device stopped before scan actually started. See DongleStopReason
